title: A few changes to get things to compile on linux.
message:
A few changes to get things to compile on linux.

1) delete local.properties.  That file shouldn't be checked-in.
(even says so inside the file :).
2) made gradlew executable
3) use correct direction of '/'s in build.gradle.
4) Replace path to OpenCV with an env variable.  I'm open to other
suggestions here, but having a hard-coded windows-style path won't work.
